<div class="title">No More Vivarin, Please!</div>
<div class="substance">Caffeine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Zonker&Exact=1">Zonker</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Zonker. "No More Vivarin, Please!: An Experience with Caffeine (exp575)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Sep 10, 2000. erowid.org/exp/575</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

